```markdown
# Peer Evaluation (template)

Please evaluate each teammate (including yourself) on the following 1–5 scale:
1 = Strongly disagree / Very poor, 5 = Strongly agree / Excellent

Fields:
- Name of evaluator:
- Team name:
- Member being evaluated:

Questions:
1. Attended team meetings and meeting deadlines (1–5)
2. Quality of contributions (1–5)
3. Helpfulness in code reviews or troubleshooting (1–5)
4. Communication & collaboration (1–5)
5. Took on meaningful responsibilities (1–5)
6. Additional comments (free text)

Submission:
- Submit the completed evaluations to the instructor (or via the provided form) by the deadline.
```
